Packit -------------------------------
The Network Injection and Capture Tool
--------------------------------------

PREREQUISITS
------------

Packit requires the following elements to compile

    autoconf >= 2.69
    libnet >= 1.1.0
    libpcap >= 0.8


INSTALLATION
------------

Packit source installation is simple:

    ./autogen.sh
    ./configure
    make

Then as 'root':

    make install


BUGS
----

Please, send your bugs to https://github.com/eribertomota/packit/issues
